description: As a part of the index family, the UBS Bloomberg SPGSCI Constant Maturity Composite GBP Monthly Hedged Total Return Index (Bloomberg Ticker: CMSPGMT Index) (the Index) tracks an investment in Commodity futures contracts based on the S&P GSCI weights using the CMCI Methodology.
name: UBS AG UBS ETC (CMCI GSCI) GBP
